title: screen_width()
brief: Retrieve the width of the screen.
seealso: screen_height
----

<p>This function will return the integer count of the number of columns the console within which <tt>lumail</tt> is running.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
-- show the width
<a href="msg.html">msg</a>( "The screen is " .. screen_width() .. " characters wide." );
</pre>